{"title_page": "William Collier (footballer)", "text_new": "{{other people||William Collier (disambiguation){{!}}William Collier}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2019}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name      = William Collier\n| fullname =\n| birth_date = 11 December 1890\n| birth_place = [[Kirkcaldy]], Scotland\n| death_date =\n| position = [[Wing half|Left half]]\n| youthyears1 =\n| youthclubs1 =\n| years1 = 1920\u20131924\n| clubs1 = [[Raith Rovers F.C.|Raith Rovers]]\n| caps1 = \n| goals1 =\n| years2 = 1924\u20131925\n| clubs2 = [[Sheffield Wednesday F.C.|Sheffield Wednesday]]\n| caps2 = \n| goals2 =\n| years3 = 1925\u2013 \n| clubs3 = [[Kettering Town F.C.|Kettering Town]]\n| caps3 = \n| goals3 = \n| totalcaps =\n| totalgoals=\n| manageryears1 = 1925\u2013\n| managerclubs1 = [[Kettering Town F.C.|Kettering Town]]\n| manageryears2 =\n| managerclubs2 = [[Dartford F.C.|Dartford]]\n| nationalyears1 = 1922\n| nationalteam1 = [[Scotland national football team|Scotland]]\n| nationalcaps1 = 1\n| nationalgoals1 = 0\n}}\n'''William Collier''' (born 11 December 1890 in [[Kirkcaldy]]) was a Scottish [[association football|footballer]], who played for [[Raith Rovers F.C.|Raith Rovers]], [[Sheffield Wednesday F.C.|Sheffield Wednesday]], [[Kettering Town F.C.|Kettering Town]] and [[Scotland national football team|Scotland]].<ref>{{harv|Smith|2013|p=52}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n;Sources\n*{{cite book | ref = harv | last=Smith | first=Paul |title=Scotland Who's Who | publisher=Pitch Publishing | year=2013 | isbn=9781909178847 }}\n\n==External links==\n*{{SFA profile}}\n*[http://www.londonhearts.com/scotland/players/williamcollier.html London Hearts profile]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Collier, William}}\n[[Category:1890 births]]\n[[Category:Year of death missing]]\n[[Category:Scottish footballers]]\n[[Category:Scotland international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football wing halves]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Kirkcaldy]]\n[[Category:Raith Rovers F.C. players