ams of [[Burnley F.C.|Burnley Football Club]]. The '''Under-23s''' currently play in the second level of reserve football in England, the [[Professional Development League#Under-23 level|Under-23 Professional Development League 2]]. The team mainly consists of players under the age of 21 at the club, but does occasionally include first team players. Burnley's '''Under-18s''' currently play in the first level of academy football in England, the [[Professional Development League#Under-18 level|U18 Professional Development League]].\n\n==U23 squad==\n{{updated|7 January 2020}}<ref name=\"Burnley FC Under 23s Player Profiles\">{{cite web |title=Under 23s |url=https://www.burnleyfootballclub.com/teams/u23-team/ |publisher=Burnley F.C. | accessdate= 30 July 2019}}</ref>\n{{fs start}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=IRL|pos=GK|name=George McMahon|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=AUS|pos=GK|name=Kai Calderbank-Park|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=DEN|pos=GK|name=Lukas Jensen|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=42|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=[[Ali Koiki]]|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Ollie Younger|other=on loan at [[St Patrick's Athletic F.C.|St Patrick's Athletic]]}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Scott Wilson|other=on loan at [[Blyth Spartans A.F.C.|Blyth Spartans]]}}\n{{fs player|no=45|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=[[Anthony Glennon]]|other=on loan at [[Grimsby Town F.C.|Grimsby Town]]}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Jordan Cropper|other=on loan at [[Chesterfield F.C.|Chesterfield]]}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Joel Senior|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Bobby Thomas|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=[[Ryan Cooney]]|other=on loan at [[Morecambe F.C.|Morecambe]]}}\n{{fs mid}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=Olatunde Bayode|other=on loan at [[Curzon Ashton F.C.|Curzon Ashton]]}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=[[Christian N'Guessan]]|other=on loan at [[Oldham Athletic A.F.C.|Oldham Athletic]]}}\n{{fs player|no=44|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=Mace Goodridge|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=[[Josh Benson]]|other=on loan at [[Grimsby Town F.C.|Grimsby Town]]}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=Vinnie Steels|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=[[Adam Phillips (footballer)|Adam Phillips]]|other=on loan at [[Morecambe F.C.|Morecambe]]}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=[[Robert Harker]]|other=on loan at [[Hartlepool United F.C.|Hartlepool United]]}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=Will Harris|other=on loan at [[Warrington Town F.C.|Warrington Town]]}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=SWE|pos=FW|name=Joel Mumbongo|other=}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=Henri Ogunby|other=}}\n{{fs end}}\n\n==U18 Squad==\n\n===Second years===\n{{fs start}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=GK|name=Lewis Thomas}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=GK|name=Harry Allen}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=SCO|pos=DF|name=Kane Patterson}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ALB|pos=DF|name=Edon Pruti}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Udoka Chima}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Matty Rain}}\n{{fs mid}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=Joe Conley}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=Rhys Fenlon}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=NIR|pos=FW|name=Chris Conn-Clarke}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=Jayden Major}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=Mitchell George}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=BER|pos=FW|name=Nejai Tucker}}\n{{fs end}}\n\n===First years===\n\n{{fs start}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Finlay Armstrong}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Joel Connolly}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Jake Rooney}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=SCO|pos=DF|name=Matty Carson}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=Dylan Moonan}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=Ben Woods}}\n{{fs mid}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=Corey Brennan}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=Tremaine Eastmond}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=Sam Unwin}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=SCO|pos=FW|name=Joe McGlynn}}\n{{fs player|no=38|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=Lewis Richardson}