m/players/burnley-fc-youth-academy|title=Burnley FC Youth Academy Graduates|last=Scholes|first=Tony|date=15 September 2016|website=UpTheClarets|access-date=22 March 2019}}</ref>\n\nPlayers that have been capped at full international level are in '''bold'''.\n{|\n|- style=\"vertical-align: top;\"\n||\n1930s\n*'''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Tommy Lawton]]'''\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ken Ashbridge]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Len Martindale]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Freddy Taylor]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[George Bray]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[George Knight (footballer, born 1921)|George Knight]]\n||\n1940s\n*'''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Peter Kippax (footballer)|Peter Kippax]]'''\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Harry Mather]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Harry Potts]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Harold Spencer]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Harold Rudman]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} Jack Knight\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Tommy Cummings]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Tommy Henderson (footballer, born 1927)|Tommy Henderson]]\n||\n1950s\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Roy Stephenson]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jimmy Adamson]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Tony Hapgood]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Albert Cheesebrough]]\n*'''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Brian Pilkington (footballer)|Brian Pilkington]]'''\n*{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Doug Winton]]\n*{{flagicon|SCO}} [[David Cargill (footballer)|David Cargill]]\n*{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Bobby Seith]]\n*'''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Colin McDonald (footballer, born 1930)|Colin McDonald]]'''\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jimmy Scott (footballer, born 1934)|Jimmy Scott]]\n*{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Dave Smith (footballer, born 1933)|Dave Smith]]\n*'''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Brian Miller (footballer)|Brian Miller]]'''\n*'''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[John Angus (footballer, born 1938)|John Angus]]'''\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jimmy Robson]]\n*'''{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Adam Blacklaw]]'''\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Des Lancaster]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ian Lawson (footballer, born 1939)|Ian Lawson]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Alan Shackleton]]\n*'''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[John Connelly (footballer)|John Connelly]]'''\n*'''{{flagicon|ENG}