odworth]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Phil Devaney]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jason Hardy]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mark Monington]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Stuart Hooper (footballer)|Stuart Hooper]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Paul McKay (footballer, born 1971)|Paul McKay]]\n||\n1990s\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Neil Howarth]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Graham Lancashire]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[John Mullin (footballer)|John Mullin]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Paul Smith (footballer, born 22 January 1976)|Paul Smith]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Wayne Dowell]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Chris Brass]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[John Borland]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Paul Weller (footballer)|Paul Weller]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Colin Carr-Lawton]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Wayne Dowell]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Phil Eastwood]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ian Duerden]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Carl Smith (footballer)|Carl Smith]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Matthew Heywood]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Chris Scott (English footballer)|Chris Scott]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Brad Maylett]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Michael Devenney]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[John Williamson (footballer, born 1981)|John Williamson]]\n||\n2000s\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Anthony Shandran]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Matthew O'Neill (footballer)|Matthew O'Neill]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Richard Chaplow]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mark Rasmussen]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Andy Waine]]\n*{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Ryan Townsend]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Paul Scott (footballer, born 1985)|Paul Scott]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Joel Pilkington]]\n*'''{{flagicon|NIR}} [[Kyle Lafferty]]'''\n*{{flagicon|IRL}} [[Chris McCann]]\n*'''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jay Rodriguez]]'''\n*{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Alex MacDonald (footballer, born 1990)|Alex MacDonald]]\n||\n2010s\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Michael King (footballer)|Michael King]]\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Wes Fletcher]]\n*'''{{flagicon|NZL}} [[Cameron Howieson]]'''\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Steven Hewitt]]\n*'''{{flagicon|NIR}} [[Shay McCartan]]'''\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Joe Jackson (footballer)|Joe Jackson]]\n*{{flagicon|AU