{"title_page": "William Cockburn (footballer)", "text_new": "{{short description|English footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2016}}\n{{Use British English|date=April 2016}}\n'''William Cockburn''' (born 1889) was an English [[association football|footballer]] who played as a defender for [[Liverpool F.C.|Liverpool]] in [[The Football League]]. Cockburn started his career at Rosehill before he moved to [[Stockport County F.C.]]. He signed for Liverpool in 1924 and appeared 18 times during his debut season. He became a regular in the team the following season as he cemented a place in the Liverpool defence and only missed six of the 42 league matches during the season. He only appeared 9 times the following season and he was transferred to [[Queens Park Rangers F.C.]] in 1928.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lfchistory.net/Players/Player/Profile/581 |title=William Cockburn |publisher=LFC History |accessdate=23 March 2012 }}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Cockburn, William}}\n[[Category:1889 births]]\n[[Category:Year of death missing]]\n[[Category:English footballers]]\n[[Category:Liverpool F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Queens Park Rangers F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Stockport County F.C. players]]\n[[Category:English Football League players]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n\n\n{{England-footy-defender-1880s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|English footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2016}}\n{{Use British English|date=April 2016}}\n'''William Cockburn''' (born 1889) was an English [[association football|footballer]] who played as a defender for [[Liverpool F.C.|Liverpool]] in [[The Football League]]. Cockburn started his career at Rosehill before he moved to [[Stockport County F.C.]]. He signed for Liverpool in 1924 and appeared 18 times during his debut season. He became a regular in the team the following season as he cemented a place in the Liverpool defence and only missed six of the 42 league matches during the season. He only appeared 9 times the following season and he was transferred to [[Queens Park Rangers F.C.]] in 1928.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lfchistory.net/Players/Player/Profile/581 |title=William Cockburn |publisher=LFC History |accessdate=23 March 2012 }}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Cockburn, William}}\n[[Category:1889 births]]\n[[Category:Year of death missing]]\n[[Category:English footballers]]\n[[Category:Liverpool F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Queens Park Rangers F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Stockport County F.C. players]]\n[[Category:English Football League players]]\n\n\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n{{England-footy-defender-1880s-stub}}\n", "name_user": "GiantSnowman", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:clean up", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Cockburn_(footballer)"}
